OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start, with rain
OL,6,Facross Cumbria and coastal stretches
OL,7,Fof the region. A few brighter breaks
OL,8,Fpossible ahead of the rain as it
OL,9,Fslowly edges eastwards through the
OL,10,Fday. Brightening up in the west later.
OL,11,FWinds easing.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain soon moving away this
OL,14,Fevening, with clear spells following.
OL,15,FA few showers are possible overnight,
OL,16,Fmainly in the north. Turning chilly
OL,17,Fwhere skies remain clear.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
